	Products tab:
		+ Find products by name, guid or vendor code
		+ Reusable controller for list of preview images - adding, removing, uploading images
		+ Set main product preview from list of previews or unique by uploading
		+ Saving of all edited product fields
		+ Add read-only guid field for selected product
		+ Add new product
		+ Remove products
		+ Categories drop down instead of text box
		+ Emphasis at products and categories which have missing categories (category was deleted earlier for example)
	
	Orders tab:
		+ Order model: guid, human-readable number, current state, log of states changes, customer phone number and email, list of products guids and actual price. Where state can be "new, paid, making up, sent, received, returned, canceled"
		Create table for orders and populate it with test orders
		View order form - list for products and its prices
		Find orders by id, phone or email, status
		Group found orders by status
		Create order form
	
	Уведомление по e-mail при новом заказе или изменения статуса заказа
	
